## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most recent research or perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not capture the full diversity of expert opinions and research in this area. Further research and updated studies would be beneficial to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the consequences of children not liking to share.